VarAttributes.VAR_NOTES: Trajectories are given as unit vectors in spherical coordinates, with phi (theta) representing the azimuthal (polar) directions, in the indicated coordinate system. They are opposite to the nominal look-direction of the instrument. Errors represent an omni-directional error. For more details about errors, contact the EDI instrument team.
